#: landview:0
msgctxt "Campaign introduction"
msgid "DzjeeAr's 6-level campaign"
msgstr "德吉尔的6关战役"

#: landview:10
msgctxt "Level introduction"
msgid "Pile of its own good. This land has never gained pain or the beauty of WAR. Everyone here is happy. You must change it immediately, my lord."
msgstr "宝物成堆。这片土地从来没有遭受过战争带来的美妙或苦难。这里的人民都很快乐。你必须立即改变这一切，我的主人。"

#: landview:11
msgctxt "Level summary"
msgid "Handful of stones. Now, this land has tasted all the wonders of pain and war. Recently, its inhabitants were happy. Now we are happy. Great job, my lord!"
msgstr "石头成堆。现在，这片土地已经饱受了战争的苦难。曾经他们快乐，而现在轮到我们快乐了。做的好，我的主人！"

#: landview:20
msgctxt "Level introduction"
msgid "Ancient Fortress. This is a splendid fortress. Many keepers tried to conquer it, but no one done it at last. It is time to change this place into ruins!"
msgstr "远古堡垒。这是一座壮观的堡垒。很多守护者都曾试图攻克它，但都没能成功。是时候把这里夷为废墟了！"

#: landview:21
msgctxt "Level summary"
msgid "Splendid ruins. In my whole poor life I haven't seen stones crushed so wonderfully, and ugly humans cut in half as you did it... Now I can see scenes from my best dreams! Good work!"
msgstr "壮观废墟。在我短暂的一生中，我从未见过石块如此完美地碎裂，以及这些丑陋的人类被你分尸的模样…现在，我终于见到了这如同美梦中的景象！干得漂亮！"

#: landview:30
msgctxt "Level introduction"
msgid "The Necromancer. This land is under rule of one Vampire, who is master in his worship.. Unfortunately, this ignorant fool refused to join our forces.. Now, it's time to show him, who will be master of this sad land."
msgstr "死灵法师。这片土地被一个吸血鬼统治，他被自己的同族所崇敬…不幸的是，这个无知的傻瓜拒绝加入我们的势力…现在，是时候让他见识一下，谁才是这片悲惨土地的主人了。"

#: landview:31
msgctxt "Level summary"
msgid "Valley of Vampires. The defeated vampire refused to acknowledge your rule.. But a few troll's hammer hits in his mutt, was enough for change his mind. I ordered him to change all local humans into vampires.. Now even children are on the DARK SIDE!"
msgstr "吸血鬼山谷。战败的吸血鬼仍然不甘心，但是几个巨魔用铁锤砸他的屁股，让他不得不屈服。我已经命令他把当地的人类全都变成了吸血鬼。现在，就连孩子们也加入了我们的邪恶阵营！"

#: landview:40
msgctxt "Level introduction"
msgid "Frozen Plains. Even the humans have left this land, in arachnophobia. They feared that giant spiders could come to their houses thru windows and eat them on dinner. Now we will bake those arthropods on supper!"
msgstr "冰冻平原。这里的人们有蜘蛛恐惧症，因此离开了这片土地。他们害怕巨大的蜘蛛从他们的窗户里爬进房间并吃掉他们当晚餐。现在，我们不如先烘烤这些蜘蛛当晚餐吧！"

#: landview:41
msgctxt "Level summary"
msgid "Warm plains. Now we can in calmness admire the sights this land, with its stirring lava drift. Spiders are crunchy, when we bake them in this hot lava long enough."
msgstr "炙热平原。现在我们可以静静地观赏这片土地沸腾的岩浆流淌的景色了。在经过这炽热岩浆长时间的烘烤之后，蜘蛛变得口感松脆。"

#: landview:50
msgctxt "Level introduction"
msgid "Barbarian Stronghold. Barbarians are horrible human nation. Before centuries, they were afraid of attacks from underground so much, that they have built this impressive stronghold. We must conquer it at all costs!"
msgstr "野蛮人根据地。野蛮人是个可怕的种族。几个世纪之前，他们因为非常惧怕地下世界的入侵，而建立了这个坚不可摧的根据地。我们必须不惜一切代价攻克它！"

#: landview:51
msgctxt "Level summary"
msgid "Keepers Stronghold. Barbarians switched to our side without any complications. Now we've got there even a circus :O My favorite trick is throwing knifes to barbarians! You should try it some day, my lord!"
msgstr "守护者根据地。野蛮人已经屈服于我们，没什么好说的。现在我们可以用他们组建一个马戏团了。哦，我最喜欢的节目是朝野蛮人扔飞刀！你有机会也应该尝试一下，我的主人！"

#: landview:60
msgctxt "Level introduction"
msgid "Final Countdown. One last step separates us from final victory. None of the keepers went to those lands before. We only know, that all the people which survived, have regrouped there. They are awaiting you.."
msgstr "终局之战。现在我们距离最终的胜利只有最后一步了。没有任何守护者层踏入过这片土地。我们只知道，所有幸存的人类残兵败将都聚集在这里。他们等待着你的到来…"

#: landview:61
msgctxt "Level summary"
msgid "Magmaland. Finally, we won! Now with the whole world conquered, at last we can go rest and relax, watching how blood and lava joyfully flows through all the plains, meadows and mountains!"
msgstr "熔岩之地。终于，我们胜利了！现在，我们已经征服了这个世界，可以去休息和享受了，并观赏鲜血和岩浆欢快地流淌在平原，草地和山脉之中的景象吧！"
